Terms and Conditions for Afaq App

1. Purpose of the Program
Afaq App is designed to manage libraries and information centers effectively, providing a comprehensive solution for library management.

2. Scope of Use

The program allows an unlimited number of users.
The number of libraries managed through the program is determined by the licensing agreement.
Data access rights are determined by the subscribing institution.

3. Privacy and Data Protection
The program adheres to strict privacy policies to ensure the protection of user and institutional data.

